{"tid":1192114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"普京買蜂蜜送給習近平 網友驚：認證維尼？","createTime":"2019-06-08T09:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T16:24:10.000Z","uid":54373,"like":76,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0fbcfb49ebe5a61e02569d4774a42fed6e926d40","tid":1192114,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:15:17.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕俄羅斯當地時間11日，即東方經濟論壇首日，在會談結束後俄羅斯總統普京與中國國家主席習近平一同參觀展覽，過程中普京買了蜂蜜給習近平，此舉讓網友大驚：「普京認證維尼」！<br />\n<br />\n《俄羅斯衛星通訊社》報導，普廷與習近平在首日會談後，一同參觀「遠東街」的展覽，兩人在俄羅斯海鮮市場攤位下廚，製作了魚子醬煎餅，和樂融融。兩人還一同逛到賣蜂蜜的攤位，此時普京買了蜂蜜給習近平，還開玩笑要習近平用人民幣付錢。<br />\n<br />\nPTT網友對此笑噴，直接聯想到習近平曾被說像小熊維尼，直說「維尼吃蜂蜜囉」、「能這樣酸習維尼的也只有聖帝了」"},{"pid":"84031279fa136d6813164ddd8503aaf6d9c8fae0","tid":1192114,"uid":54824,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.disneyclips.com/images2/images/07114.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.disneyclips.com%2Fimages2%2Fimages%2F07114.gif&h=70181669&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59d550f36fbf90ca4d0fad1e258f0dfbe5eb30c3","tid":1192114,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f05f14573ad98618927809f24128848aeb0beef","tid":1192114,"uid":45914,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:24:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"523867471f37d118d37f6fdae5baeeeadde24c7a","tid":1192114,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:28:55.000Z","msg":"睇怕「蜜、密、蜂、峰」都變敏感詞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad28fa8a8bbab336622a8b9f7b938ea38cbfc4d6","tid":1192114,"uid":101110,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=