le=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑色三毛警告信號現正生效 6月8日16時</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過70次/禁70次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備時項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待明天遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b251b99ad0da001df74c9611f374b672b5570ec9","tid":1192114,"uid":55533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://www.disneyclips.com/images2/images/07114.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.disneyclips.com%2Fimages2%2Fimages%2F07114.gif&h=70181669&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似h動啲女俾人抽插完再射到成身都係然後抹啲精入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9077af3c633c5f90a9c50f20c6ac8e26baddef1e","tid":1192114,"uid":234811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:54:00.000Z","msg":"毛就滅麻雀<br />\n習幾時滅蜜蜂?"},{"pid":"a38b77adaefb480cdd3a82cf3dbbdd54b41255c0","tid":1192114,"uid":212796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:57:30.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;遠東&rdquo;街？<br />\n海參崴音名都唔用了？"},{"pid":"ce9bb3879736b3632cff9c58cd36df96c253721f","tid":